      public Document(String userId, String clientId, org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile file, String docId, String title, int wordCount) throws IOException
      Constructs a Document object with the specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      userId - The unique user ID associated with this document.
      clientId - The client ID or identifier for the document.
      file - The MultipartFile object representing the document's content.
